    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNo built-in way to delete a buffer while preserving the window layout\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nAn API or ex-command to delete a buffer while preserving window layout. Like these plugins:\n\n- https://github.com/echasnovski/mini.bufremove\n- https://github.com/folke/snacks.nvim/blob/main/docs/bufdelete.md\n- https://github.com/famiu/bufdelete.nvim\n\nThe discussion in #33314 suggests deprecating `nvim_buf_delete()` in favor of a new `nvim_buf_del()`. Maybe it's worth considering adding this capability to `nvim_buf_del()` ",
